{"tid":2191744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"跪 求 抵 制 T V B 戰 線 管 理 員 入","createTime":"2020-09-06T15:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T06:38:56.000Z","uid":90800,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8b63bdc01415dffc257a22f26743c48c4d81b6","tid":2191744,"uid":90800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"自問我冇你地嘅鬼才，麻煩你地運用無限創意開Post抵制人血蛋糕店，救救港人！！<br />\n<br />\n人血蛋糕店叫：<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>The One Bakery</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4SzxHL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4SzxHL.jpg&h=d2e027d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢食曬2邊茶禮，彈出彈入。<br />\n最重要係：<strong><span class=\"red\">和你Pay係無佢資料  好多人中招</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRjieVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRjieVy.jpg&h=12cb0618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/theonebakery2015/?locale2=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Ftheonebakery2015%2F%3Flocale2%3Dzh_HK&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4jBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=9d2c26cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/theonebakery2015/?locale2=zh_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">時序:</span></span></strong><br />\n上年8月借舖俾CCTVB拍劇，仲好自豪放FB<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPb8B8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPb8B8E.jpg&h=a1353b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10月開始人血整PEPE蛋糕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KOz6oPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOz6oPE.jpg&h=fca30692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年3月加入送埋蛋糕俾黑警新劇做道具<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qp0hvwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQp0hvwf.jpg&h=d2615131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你以為佢一心做藍店時，其實佢彈出彈入，你吹咩！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E37cjpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE37cjpY.jpg&h=ff9f3c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最黎附上丁圖一張以表誠意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uno68kE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Funo68kE.jpg&h=9111dc04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76d6094759cb3b59de6e15948fa7d0e5ba27750d","tid":2191744,"uid":90800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"6b42023abcc8dd57e88b1c2236656a5beed265f5","tid":2191744,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecdae988a2882dc92a516050828ffe0b274cea2","tid":2191744,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"TUI"},{"pid":"84a3fe850495b8d0d59d7db6116f79881deb533b","tid":2191744,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:40:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edac4954da47757c76542c1a0a4e4ef13348b396","tid":2191744,"uid":201274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:41:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2ceea166aeda398ad76e098dea4969714f59d0","tid":2191744,"uid":90800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"拍攝時已有2個後生係門口望緊蛋糕，雖然我唔肯定佢地係咪黃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1Hr8pp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1Hr8pp.jpg&h=e4112c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https:/